# Frontend (React)

- Vite + MUI + TanStack Query + react-i18next. API client: `frontend/src/services/apiClient.ts`.
- Env: `VITE_API_BASE_URL` (must include `/api/v1`), `VITE_SOCKET_URL` for Socket.IO.
- RBAC: `ProtectedRoute` + `menuConfig.ts` + shared permissions in `frontend/src/shared/rbac/`.
- Do not import from `backend/` — use local `frontend/src/shared/` copy of types/constants.
- Pages are lazy-loaded in `AppRouter.tsx`. Admin-only routes under `/app/admin/*`.
- Export reports via `useExport` hook (Excel, CSV, PDF).
- Health polling: use `healthService.ts`; do not confuse Socket.IO status with MQTT status.
- After edits: `cd frontend && npm run build`.
